experiment 5:Delete
the NULL constraint of ‘age’ in the STUDENT table.

mysql> alter table student modify age int null;
Query OK, 0 rows affected (1.04 sec)
Records: 0  Duplicates: 0  Warnings: 0

mysql> desc student;
