experiment 6:Change
the table name EMPLOYEE as PERSON

mysql> drop table person;
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.17 sec)

mysql> alter table employee rename to person;
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.12 sec)

mysql> desc person;
